CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 11, 1958, page 3, reads: "Congratulations! - Dr. William D. McClelland is congratulated by his deputy coroner, Albert Charles, after being sworn in for a fifth term last week as coroner of Allegheny County. - Teenie Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Allegheny County Coroner, Dr. William D. McClelland shaking hands with deputy coroner, Albert Charles, standing in interior with a landscape painting and furniture with flowers, lamp, and newspaper that reads "Estimates"
